'''Ava''' is a medical student who came to the recruitment fair.

==History==
Ava was in medical school when she attended a recruitment fair to look at hospitals where she could apply for residency. After watching Levi and Mabel's presentation on The Webber Method, she asked if that meant residents were unsurpervised. Levi clarified that they weren't and tried to explain how it was better for residents. Ava didn't understand how it was any different from any other program and left when she got a message that her personalized tote bag was ready at another booth.
